Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.19,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using the power of Lífþrasir is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.10,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}essentially shaving off \Na part of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:23.55,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When he runs out of energy, he will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.94,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saito will die?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.51,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten pretty good at this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:32.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want him to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:39.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, don't let anything \Nactually threaten the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.96,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(275,1)}The Awakening of Calamity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:37.27,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, Miss Vallière, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.33,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I know you were up very late \Nlast night, but you should
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:41.81,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,still get up soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:46.91,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Siesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.22,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.16,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.22,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.06,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:03:00.76,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time you realized \Nthat you're a terrible liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.18,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, Saito is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:08.30,CRZero,Aneas,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.33,CRZero,Aneas,0000,0000,0000,,Is Miss Vallière awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.34,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.84,CRZero,Aneas,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Henrietta has summoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:16.61,CRZero,Aneas,0000,0000,0000,,I need Miss Vallière, Miss Westwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.98,CRZero,Aneas,0000,0000,0000,,and Saito to come with me at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.82,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:23.85,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.08,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:42.38,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, Saito, \NLouise, and Tiffania.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:43.33,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:48.36,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,His Holiness sent a messenger \Nwhen he returned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.97,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,to Romalia after the \Ncoronation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:53.27,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,The message was that he wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:55.77,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,the three of you to go to \NRomalia as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,To Romalia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.76,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:03:59.82,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,It seems
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:05.91,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,that a village at the foot \Nof the Fire Dragon mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.78,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,was destroyed overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.69,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:15.23,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not certain, only that \Nsomething terrible has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.63,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,If His Holiness thinks your \Npresence is necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:19.47,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,it might mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:26.49,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to look so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.87,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But, Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.81,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go and see for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:32.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we can refuse \NHis Holiness, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.42,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.83,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm counting on you, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.41,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Julio will come meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:42.81,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,once you're near Aquileia's border.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:43.93,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.39,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Queen Charlotte to \Naid you with a dragon, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.90,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:52.17,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,When my sister heard about this, \Nshe was worried, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.75,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to do you a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:57.79,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,and carry you to Romalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.21,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:04.35,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,You should consider yourself \Nlucky that a proud
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:06.41,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,rhyme dragon is doing this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.08,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.39,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:19.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,We will. Please keep \Nan eye on things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.11,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.67,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what exactly is happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.24,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.20,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're back in des Ornières,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:36.25,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,we can eat, take baths and \Nfight over the beds again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:40.28,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,And then we'll all grow old together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:43.39,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,If you believe it, it will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.22,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:48.68,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,So please, come home quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:52.16,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, Miss Westwood, and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:55.17,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:02.30,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.73,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.74,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Julio is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:23.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.54,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.80,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,No... Hurry, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.48,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The city, it's... \NBut that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:44.88,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's Aquileia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.41,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.37,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,We have to help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:07.04,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pal, they're \Ncoming from the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.53,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.61,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.28,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're not \Nin their right minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:22.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:27.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.09,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, fly up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:31.25,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Sylphid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.13,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.51,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:45.92,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:46.73,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Julio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:47.95,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.64,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.49,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we've got \Nto get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.65,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it's too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Julio, what's with those dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:06.03,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,All the dragons in this \Nregion went insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.08,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I've managed to keep this one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:11.37,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,under control using my Windalfr powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.66,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about Sylphid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.76,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Rhyme dragons are not \Nlike ordinary dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.71,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But why on earth did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.95,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,The noxious gases coming out \Nof his body are causing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,His?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:45.17,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.15,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,It's the legendary dragon of old...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:49.68,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,The Ancient Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.32,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,As you all know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:07.29,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,the Ancient Dragon has \Nsuddenly appeared and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:09.69,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,it has leveled Aquileia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:13.12,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,And now that monster is headed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:15.45,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,towards the sacred city of Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.13,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Do not be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:21.28,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,If we use all our strength, \Nwe can certainly defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:24.38,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Before the Ancient Dragon \Nreaches our city,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.54,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,we will strike at the Valley of Oltia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.45,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,You holy knights blessed by the \Nstrength of our founder Brimir,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.68,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,now is the time to \Nshow us your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.52,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let this holy city be defiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.71,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the innocent people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.03,CRZero,People,0000,0000,0000,,Long live His Holiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:44.01,CRZero,People,0000,0000,0000,,Our founder Brimir will protect us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.53,CRZero,People,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.54,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Your Holiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.28,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I have brought them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.95,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:08.69,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Your Holiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:12.42,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,we saw Aquileia burn and there \Nwas nothing we could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:17.00,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,That monster suddenly appeared \Nfrom the Fire Dragon mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:20.83,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,We immediately told the \Npeople to evacuate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:24.61,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Your Holiness, could it be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.01,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,that this is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:28.60,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,The danger threatening the world \Nthat you were worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.59,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid it might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.11,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing the \Nancient texts say about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.77,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,the World Crisis is that \Nit is "a great calamity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.45,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,that charred the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:42.11,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Many scholars, myself included,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:44.98,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,have spent much time \Nstudying this subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.51,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,The theory that it is a \Ngiant dragon did exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:49.93,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,but there was no firm evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:52.63,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,However, now there's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:56.30,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,We must stop that monster at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:11:00.84,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,This is the time for us Void \NMages to join forces
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.64,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,to prevent more innocent \Nblood from being spilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.05,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,We have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.16,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:12.73,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Your Explosion spell \Nis crucial to our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.55,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, all will rest on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.23,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.41,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.23,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,according to the reports we have,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:23.53,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,the dragon's body is veiled \Nin a shroud of miasma,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.51,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,a magic barrier, \Nthat reflects offensive spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.00,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,First we have to negate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that with my Dispel spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:33.62,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will take care of that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.47,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,We need to preserve your \Nstrength as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:38.98,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Westwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:44.70,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,please cast your Mind Wipe \Non the dragon's minions
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.58,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,and protect the holy knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.89,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:53.38,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Saito, there is something \NI must ask of you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.54,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you utilize...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.98,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,your Lífþrasir powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:01.82,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:02.67,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:04.08,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Think about this first...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What is there to think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.51,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do everything \Nin my power to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:15.58,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you from the very \Nbottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:23.05,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us head to the Oltia Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.29,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.65,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Our farsight magic has
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.45,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,revealed that the dragon \Nis only 30 leagues away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.79,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:50.79,CRZero,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,But why is the dragon \Ngoing for the Holy City?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.99,CRZero,Knight2,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows, maybe something \Nis drawing him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.54,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Your Holiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.49,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:04.39,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Saito isn't going to die \Nin the battle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.99,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I mean by using his Lífþrasir power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.47,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,This makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.48,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.42,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,you had nothing but \Nhatred for the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.07,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,and could not love anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:18.31,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of boy you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.98,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you came to live with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:24.49,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,you still had your \Nreservations, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.03,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,And now you've become
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:29.02,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,someone who expresses \Nconcern for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.78,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I truly believe that sending you to the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.75,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Academy was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:39.72,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,You are my pride and joy, \NJulio Chesaré.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.97,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Your Holiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:45.09,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt the power of Lífþrasir
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:47.81,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,will vanish after \Nusing it once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.39,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,However, the more it's used,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.06,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,the faster his death will approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.36,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why we must make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:57.38,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,this plan succeeds on the first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:13:59.85,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.65,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I guess their plan is to lure \Nthe dragon into the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.72,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,and slow it down by \Ndestroying the cliffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:08.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it has a magic barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.80,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,physical attacks might \Nbe able to get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:13.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.40,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,If only the rocket launcher \NI used back then was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.80,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.51,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.97,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to help His Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:24.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.60,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Do not use your Lífþrasir power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.12,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use it ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:33.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But that power can amplify Void magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.05,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,At the expense of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.44,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Lífþrasir \Ncan't be replenished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's used up, the familiar dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:49.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:52.30,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,His Holiness said so himself, \Nso I know it must be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:57.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm really going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:15:01.51,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I... So that's what Lífþrasir is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.22,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:07.48,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.29,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something about \Nhim with my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.66,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.95,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.43,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,This is because I made \NSaito into a familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:27.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But, Tiffa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.21,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.29,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:31.69,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.31,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Don't falter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.72,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.37,CRZero,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.90,CRZero,Knight2,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show you the power \Nof the Holy Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.50,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:14.20,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the only one who \Nmight die in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:19.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow myself \Nto cower in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But, Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.93,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I am also a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:25.67,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I must protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.33,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Including you, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:30.48,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:34.11,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, it's almost time. Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:36.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.37,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.19,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, look after Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:44.50,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this over with, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:47.10,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.18,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.45,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Keep attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.94,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Show no fear! We are holy knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the Mind \NWipe spell worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:49.99,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.93,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Louise, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.68,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:00.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we just have to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.05,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Like Siesta said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.93,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We have to believe we can \Nall go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:25.72,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Cano Soil Teiwas Isa Unjo \NCebo Ragsjur Dagas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:36.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.63,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's Cleansing magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:43.45,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Normally it's healing magic, \Nbut for evil beings,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.14,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,this magic is more \Ndamaging than an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.27,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, this is my Void magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:51.38,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Saito, if you would be so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.62,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.60,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even as we watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:14.63,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saito's life is being depleted. \NI... I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.00,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:30.65,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Founder Brimir, lend me your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.82,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pal, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:40.12,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This... This is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.36,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:01.35,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Fly up! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:07.49,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Something's strange... Sylphid, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.11,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Use me, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:17.59,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:36.71,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, pal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.69,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this one's a \Nlittle too strong for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:47.70,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you looked pretty \Ndopey the first time we met,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.53,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,but you've shaped up quite nicely,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.51,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:53.97,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Derf!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.63,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,So long, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.41,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.63,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this... Derf...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:21.06,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:31.33,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:36.34,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Julio,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.78,CRZero,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,you have to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.50,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Your Holiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.44,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Your Holiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:29.62,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Saito, there's something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:32.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to \Ntell you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:35.62,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So today, I'm finally going to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:37.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, stay tuned \Nfor "Louise's Choice."
